      "@type": "LcaStudy",
      "sectionTitle": "POTENTIAL ENVIRONMENTAL IMPACTS PER REFERENCE FLOW",
      "functionalUnit": "The results are provided for coverage of 1m2 using Dragocryl Velouté sup airless.",
      "systemBoundaries": "System boundaries (parsed from PDF diagram — no AI)\nPage 7\nDeclared modules (☒): A1, A2, A3, A4, A5, B1, B2, B3, B4, B5, B6, B7, C1, C2, C3, C4, D\nNot declared (☐): —\nBy life-cycle stage:\nProduct stage: A1, A2, A3\nConstruction installation stage: A4, A5\nUse stage: B1, B2, B3, B4, B5, B6, B7\nEnd of life stage: C1, C2, C3, C4\nBeyond the system boundaries: D\n\nModule labels (vertical text):\nA1: materials\nA2: Transport\nA3: Manufacturing\nA4: Transport\nA5: installation\nB1: Use\nB2: Maintenance\nB3: Repair\nB4: Replacement\nB5: Refurbishment\nB6: use\nB7: use\nC1: construction\nC2: Transport\nC3: processing\nC4: Disposal\nD: Recovery",
